Neither his wife, nor him.
也不认识他妻子

26
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,680
So be it.
就这样吧

27
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:15,800
Whoever killed him, must know you, then.
不管谁杀了他  凶手一定认识你  然后……

28
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,280
Think about it.
思考一下

29
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:22,800
Who is able to commit such a thing around you?
你身边谁能做出这种事情？

30
