Wouldn't that be awesome?
那不是很棒吗？

107
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,800
If we forget everything wrong,
如果我们忘记所有错误

108
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:23,080
and only remember the correct things?
只记得正确的事情？

109
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,600
But don't you worry.
但是你不用担心

110
